#: ../../appendix/upgrade-notes/2.x-to-3.0.rst:432
msgid "Metadata no longer has an ``owner_guid``. It is no longer possible to query metadata based on ``owner_guids``. Subsequently, ``ElggMetadata::canEdit()`` will always return ``true`` regardless of the logged in user, unless explicitly overriden by a plugin hook."
